<h1 local-id=3D"f65d0b90c3af" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-1.Projek=
t=C3=A1ttekint=C3=A9s">1. Projekt =C3=A1ttekint=C3=A9s</h1>
<p local-id=3D"9c9c62830fe8">A Planova egy t=C3=B6bbplatformos napt=C3=A1ra=
lkalmaz=C3=A1s, amelynek frontend oldala k=C3=A9t<br>
klienst tartalmaz:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"82f443c9f46b">
<li local-id=3D"9951c45b7dd8">
<p local-id=3D"80a7b4b7d5e0">Web alkalmaz=C3=A1s (Next.js + Tamagui)</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"3eeb9d5bfd7e">
<p local-id=3D"4441ffba4919">Mobil alkalmaz=C3=A1s (Expo + React Native + T=
amagui) *</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4d9cd69351ee">Mindk=C3=A9t kliens ugyanazokat a megosztott c=
somagokat (packages) haszn=C3=A1lja, ami<br>
biztos=C3=ADtja a k=C3=B3d =C3=BAjrafelhaszn=C3=A1lhat=C3=B3s=C3=A1g=C3=A1t=
 =C3=A9s az egys=C3=A9ges =C3=BCzleti logik=C3=A1t. A<br>
projekt monorepo strukt=C3=BAr=C3=A1t alkalmaz pnpm workspace =C3=A9s Turbo=
repo seg=C3=ADts=C3=A9g=C3=A9vel.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7cceebe6d9e1">Az alkalmaz=C3=A1s neve: Planova<br>
Le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: Felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3-k=C3=B6zpont=C3=BA napt=C3=A1ralkal=
maz=C3=A1s</p>
