=A9rhet=C5=91 el: @repo/&lt;csomag_n=C3=A9v&gt;</p>
<p local-id=3D"702424518539">packages/api/ =E2=86=92 @repo/api<br>
 packages/config/ =E2=86=92 @repo/config<br>
 packages/features/ =E2=86=92 @repo/features<br>
 packages/hooks/ =E2=86=92 @repo/hooks<br>
 packages/types/ =E2=86=92 @repo/types<br>
 packages/ui/ =E2=86=92 @repo/ui<br>
 packages/utils/ =E2=86=92 @repo/utils</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"36cce873700b" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-4.Megosz=
tottcsomagokr=C3=A9szletesle=C3=ADr=C3=A1sa">4. Megosztott csomagok r=C3=A9=
szletes le=C3=ADr=C3=A1sa</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"686c875fbc6a" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-4.1.@rep=
o/api=E2=80=93APIkommunik=C3=A1ci=C3=B3sr=C3=A9teg">4.1. @repo/api =E2=80=
=93 API kommunik=C3=A1ci=C3=B3s r=C3=A9teg</h2>
<p local-id=3D"1b67766ecce1">Az API csomag felel=C5=91s a backend-del val=
=C3=B3 minden HTTP kommunik=C3=A1ci=C3=B3=C3=A9rt.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6f605535d330">F=C3=A1jlok:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"afe0c124ddb0">
<li local-id=3D"79c7bf938f45">
<p local-id=3D"0c72b60ecd92">api.ts - Axios instance konfigur=C3=A1l=C3=A1s=
a, interceptorok</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9eb6e2910b01">
<p local-id=3D"0f879418d922">auth.ts - Autentik=C3=A1ci=C3=B3s v=C3=A9gpont=
ok (signUp, signIn, signOut,<br>
 verify, refresh)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4674e0b8f0cb">
<p local-id=3D"285fe03d2907">calendar.ts - Napt=C3=A1r CRUD m=C5=B1veletek =
(getCalendar, createCalendar,<br>
 updateCalendar, deleteCalendar)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"00836df1b270">
<p local-id=3D"646c9186af67">calendarEntry.ts - Napt=C3=A1rbejegyz=C3=A9s C=
RUD (getCalendarEntry,<br>
 createCalendarEntry, updateCalendarEntry,<br>
 deleteCalendarEntry)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0216c51611a0">
<p local-id=3D"3244980edd7f">profile.ts - Profil m=C5=B1veletek (getProfile=
, updateProfile)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"349c8f55291e">
<p local-id=3D"92160392b05d">notification.ts - Bar=C3=A1t k=C3=A9r=C3=A9s k=
=C3=BCld=C3=A9se (sendFriendRequest)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e304d4c47c06">
<p local-id=3D"b66a6f7bd667">nativeTokenStorage.ts - Token t=C3=A1rol=C3=A1=
s kezel=C3=A9se (nat=C3=ADv vs. web)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5a3eb9146f52">Axios instance jellemz=C5=91k:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4e88e657060c">
<li local-id=3D"f6c49fc5c669">
<p local-id=3D"70f7d677484b">Alap URL: <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"h=
ttp://localhost:8080" rel=3D"nofollow">http://localhost:8080</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b54f029831d">
<p local-id=3D"8830cd1680a0">Web: cookie-alap=C3=BA hiteles=C3=ADt=C3=A9s (=
withCredentials: true)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3e95e8e5793c">
<p local-id=3D"2ce01af893f8">Nat=C3=ADv: Bearer token hiteles=C3=ADt=C3=A9s=
 (expo-secure-store)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e476755c3b8">
<p local-id=3D"7b5609d2e091">Automatikus token friss=C3=ADt=C3=A9s intercep=
torral (401-es hiba eset=C3=A9n)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"37707507bb80">
