<h2 local-id=3D"5dbde492014f" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-4.2.@rep=
o/hooks=E2=80=93=C3=81llapotkezel=C3=A9s(Zustandstore-ok=C3=A9sReactQueryho=
ok-ok)">4.2. @repo/hooks =E2=80=93 =C3=81llapotkezel=C3=A9s (Zustand store-=
ok =C3=A9s React Query hook-ok)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"87f85407d809">Zustand store-ok:</p>
<p local-id=3D"5df6e763e306">useAuthStore<br>
 =C3=81llapot: isAuthorized, isLoading<br>
 M=C5=B1veletek: verifyAuth() =E2=80=93 token =C3=A9rv=C3=A9nyes=C3=ADt=C3=
=A9s =C3=A9s automatikus refresh<br>
 Folyamat: verify() =E2=86=92 hiba eset=C3=A9n refresh() =E2=86=92 hiba ese=
t=C3=A9n isAuthorized=3Dfalse</p>
<p local-id=3D"73af8f70e50f">useCalendarStore<br>
 =C3=81llapot: currentDate, selectedDate, viewType, checkedCalendarIds,<br>
 tabletView, mobileView, hideSidebar<br>
 N=C3=A9zet t=C3=ADpusok: "month" | "multiweek" | "week" | "day"<br>
 Navig=C3=A1ci=C3=B3: decMonth/incMonth, decWeek/incWeek, decDay/incDay,<br=
>
 decYear/incYear, resetToToday<br>
 Reszponzivit=C3=A1s: initResizeListener() =E2=80=93 ablakm=C3=A9ret v=C3=
=A1ltoz=C3=A1s figyel=C3=A9se<br>
 (768px=3Dmobil, 1024px=3Dtablet)</p>
<p local-id=3D"f9785e65ceb3">useProfileStore<br>
 =C3=81llapot: locale (Intl.Locale), weekStartsOn, hour12<br>
 Perzisztencia: localStorage-ba menti a be=C3=A1ll=C3=ADt=C3=A1sokat<br>
 Napt=C3=A1r kezd=C5=91napja: "monday" | "sunday"<br>
 =C3=93ra form=C3=A1tum: 12 =C3=B3r=C3=A1s vagy 24 =C3=B3r=C3=A1s</p>
<p local-id=3D"c1ee89b0e234">useContextMenuStore<br>
 Jobb-klikk kontextus men=C3=BC kezel=C3=A9se<br>
 =C3=81llapot: position, display, contextMenuOpen, fieldType, date<br>
 T=C3=ADpusok: "cell" (=C3=BCres cella) | "schedule" (megl=C3=A9v=C5=91 bej=
egyz=C3=A9s)</p>
<p local-id=3D"92e4af0a8eb7">useDialogStore<br>
 Felugr=C3=B3 dial=C3=B3gus ablakok kezel=C3=A9se<br>
 =C3=81llapot: isDialogOpen, title, description, content (React node)</p>
<p local-id=3D"a24a4cae3b0d">useNavbarStore<br>
 Navig=C3=A1ci=C3=B3s s=C3=A1v =C3=A1llapota (be=C3=A1ll=C3=ADt=C3=A1sok pa=
nel nyitva/z=C3=A1rva)</p>
<p local-id=3D"61f7c21c5778">useNotificationStore<br>
 SignalR kapcsolat kezel=C3=A9se (val=C3=B3s idej=C5=B1 =C3=A9rtes=C3=ADt=
=C3=A9sek)<br>
 =C3=81llapot: connection, notifications, isConnected<br>
 SignalR Hub: /notifications v=C3=A9gpont<br>
 Automatikus =C3=BAjracsatlakoz=C3=A1s (.withAutomaticReconnect())<br>
 Web: cookie-kat haszn=C3=A1l | Nat=C3=ADv: access token-t k=C3=BCld</p>
<p local-id=3D"c05fb97e765b">React Query hook-ok:</p>
<p local-id=3D"d136b0af862e">useCalendars<br>
 Lek=C3=A9ri az =C3=B6sszes napt=C3=A1rat (GET api/Calendar)<br>
 Cache: 5 perc staleTime<br>
 Query kulcs: ["myCalendars"]</p>
<p local-id=3D"69da8f7d4e38">useCalendarEntries<br>
 Lek=C3=A9ri a napt=C3=A1rak bejegyz=C3=A9seit (p=C3=A1rhuzamos k=C3=A9r=C3=
=A9sek minden napt=C3=A1rnak)<br>
 Felt=C3=A9tel: myCalendarsQuery.data el=C3=A9rhet=C5=91s=C3=A9ge<br>
 Cache: 5 perc staleTime<br>
 Query kulcs: ["calendarEntries", calendarIds]</p>
<p local-id=3D"9c310df55b57">useProfile<br>
 Profil adatok lek=C3=A9r=C3=A9se</p>
