<h2 local-id=3D"3f7db42f1b00" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-5.2.Hite=
les=C3=ADt=C3=A9sifolyamat">5.2. Hiteles=C3=ADt=C3=A9si folyamat</h2>
<p local-id=3D"cac75b161354">Bejelentkez=C3=A9s (SignInForm):</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"825af504976c">
<li local-id=3D"63fa6d89af65">
<p local-id=3D"4fd75e2a2db4">Felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3 megadja az email c=C3=AD=
met =C3=A9s jelsz=C3=B3t</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c388c624c4ce">
<p local-id=3D"236c3c0a0468">Zod valid=C3=A1ci=C3=B3 ellen=C5=91rzi a mez=
=C5=91 kit=C3=B6lt=C3=B6tts=C3=A9g=C3=A9t</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a14485634ce">
<p local-id=3D"831fdd77a9b5">signIn() API h=C3=ADv=C3=A1s (POST api/auth/si=
gn-in)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"06b576a64b16">
<p local-id=3D"8c743082046b">Webre: a szerver cookie-kat =C3=A1ll=C3=ADt be=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cde3ba248d47">
<p local-id=3D"7cf74a6c63fd">Nativra: accessToken + refreshToken t=C3=A1rol=
=C3=B3dik SecureStore-ban</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1a750b2b75d7">
<p local-id=3D"3b620f84cb95">Sikeres bejelentkez=C3=A9s ut=C3=A1n: =C3=A1ti=
r=C3=A1ny=C3=ADt=C3=A1s a /calendar oldalra</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"ace103bc1e95">Regisztr=C3=A1ci=C3=B3 (SignUpForm):</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e3b86482d425">
<li local-id=3D"0bae102e00f1">
<p local-id=3D"fb44724c9ba1">Email + jelsz=C3=B3 valid=C3=A1ci=C3=B3 (er=C5=
=91s jelsz=C3=B3 k=C3=B6vetelm=C3=A9ny)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dc2c4f9282d5">
<p local-id=3D"e4cd8688745b">signUp() API h=C3=ADv=C3=A1s (POST api/auth/si=
gn-up)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"78c4fb47bdfd">
<p local-id=3D"8ff40ef37bd6">Automatikus bejelentkez=C3=A9s a signIn() h=C3=
=ADv=C3=A1ssal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c7aac196aec9">
<p local-id=3D"dacc78845af2">=C3=81tir=C3=A1ny=C3=ADt=C3=A1s a /calendar ol=
dalra</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"db81849ffd10">Kijelentkez=C3=A9s:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"5361918ac465">
<li local-id=3D"b0b2b465775d">
<p local-id=3D"f5c24b5c7244">Token-ek t=C3=B6rl=C3=A9se (SecureStore vagy c=
ookie)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb17ad4ce71c">
<p local-id=3D"3d70b06756c2">signOut API h=C3=ADv=C3=A1s (GET api/auth/sign=
-out)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"799c71cbe397">
<p local-id=3D"64f5d7d112c5">=C3=81tir=C3=A1ny=C3=ADt=C3=A1s a /sign-in old=
alra (window.location.href)</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 local-id=3D"345df04186bf" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-5.3.Napt=
=C3=A1rn=C3=A9zetek">5.3. Napt=C3=A1r n=C3=A9zetek</h2>
<p local-id=3D"473c4ef09f34">A napt=C3=A1r n=C3=A9gy k=C3=BCl=C3=B6nb=C3=B6=
z=C5=91 n=C3=A9zetet t=C3=A1mogat:</p>
<p local-id=3D"53a67d6a99c3">Havi n=C3=A9zet ("month"):<br>
 - 5 vagy 6 hetes r=C3=A1cs (35 vagy 42 cella)<br>
 - H=C3=A9t sz=C3=A1mok az oldals=C3=A1vban<br>
 - El=C5=91z=C5=91/k=C3=B6vetkez=C5=91 havi napok halv=C3=A1ny=C3=ADtva<br>
 - G=C3=B6rg=C5=91s navig=C3=A1ci=C3=B3 (mousewheel)</p>
<p local-id=3D"ba29bade78b3">T=C3=B6bbhetes n=C3=A9zet ("multiweek"):<br>
 - 4 hetes r=C3=A1cs (28 cella)<br>
 - Az aktu=C3=A1lis h=C3=A9t a kiv=C3=A1lasztott d=C3=A1tum alapj=C3=A1n</p=
>
<p local-id=3D"66d939b85442">Heti n=C3=A9zet ("week"):<br>
 - 7 nap, =C3=B3ra-alap=C3=BA r=C3=A1cs (0-23 =C3=B3ra)<br>
 - Oldalra g=C3=B6rgethet=C5=91 tartalom</p>
<p local-id=3D"a0ac2914e554">Napi n=C3=A9zet ("day"):<br>
 - 1 nap, 24 =C3=B3r=C3=A1s r=C3=A1cs<br>
 - R=C3=A9szletes id=C5=91beoszt=C3=A1s megjelen=C3=ADt=C3=A9s</p>
<p local-id=3D"41b8b7a101ea">Navig=C3=A1ci=C3=B3:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"eb81e259f5f0">
<li local-id=3D"ac59adb93fb3">
<p local-id=3D"0d266566064e">El=C5=91z=C5=91/k=C3=B6vetkez=C5=91 gombokkal =
(ny=C3=ADlak)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e98054a62778">
<p local-id=3D"6c66da8f905c">Eg=C3=A9rg=C3=B6rg=C5=91vel (havi n=C3=A9zetbe=
n)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cd2bc3609eba">
<p local-id=3D"33c676b92554">"Ma" gombbal (resetToToday)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94685abd39a4">
<p local-id=3D"d552926d0809">N=C3=A9zet t=C3=ADpus v=C3=A1lt=C3=B3 (leg=C3=
=B6rd=C3=BCl=C5=91 men=C3=BC)</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"54794546084e" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-5.4.Olda=
ls=C3=A1v(Sidebar)">5.4. Oldals=C3=A1v (Sidebar)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"64df34924d75">Az oldals=C3=A1v tartalmazza:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ba7b1fac8263">
<li local-id=3D"35a8d118c786">
<p local-id=3D"dc667e36127c">DatePicker: mini napt=C3=A1r a d=C3=A1tumv=C3=
=A1laszt=C3=A1shoz</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"522f97942786">
<p local-id=3D"a83d0c0fe562">Napt=C3=A1rlista: a felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3 napt=
=C3=A1rai checkbox-okkal</p>
<ul local-id=3D"582bdfd8cd29">
<li local-id=3D"800640dd00ed">
<p local-id=3D"a4703d6fded1">Napt=C3=A1r sz=C3=ADn jelz=C3=A9se</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"215cb3da0fe0">
<p local-id=3D"aaaabe4304a2">Napt=C3=A1r szerkeszt=C3=A9se (n=C3=A9v, sz=C3=
=ADn m=C3=B3dos=C3=ADt=C3=A1s)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d67bfc22508b">
<p local-id=3D"4b0d7b62a06a">Napt=C3=A1r t=C3=B6rl=C3=A9se</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f55f92660a8">
<p local-id=3D"2f57757d3c95">=C3=9Aj napt=C3=A1r l=C3=A9trehoz=C3=A1sa (Cal=
endarPlus ikon + CreateCalendarForm)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b345e04a9d12">
<p local-id=3D"1205c6a3a5b2">Reszponz=C3=ADv: tablet n=C3=A9zetben elrejthe=
t=C5=91 (hamburger men=C3=BC)</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"c2f3b0f77285" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-5.5.Napt=
=C3=A1rbejegyz=C3=A9sek">5.5. Napt=C3=A1rbejegyz=C3=A9sek</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8d7d452bf8e5">Bejegyz=C3=A9s l=C3=A9trehoz=C3=A1sa:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e47c5fa538f4">
<li local-id=3D"e4b4e798138e">
<p local-id=3D"7a111da100c3">Jobb-klikk egy cell=C3=A1ra =E2=86=92 kontextu=
s men=C3=BC =E2=86=92 "New Event"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1546ff601fbc">
<p local-id=3D"7792552c792a">Vagy a napi/heti n=C3=A9zetben "+" gomb</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"f1e18235d78a">
<p local-id=3D"9858aab13475">CreateCalendarEntryForm megny=C3=ADlik dial=C3=
=B3gusban</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb1f4234afe0">
<p local-id=3D"b992cbe9335e">Mez=C5=91k: napt=C3=A1r kiv=C3=A1laszt=C3=A1s,=
 kateg=C3=B3ria, n=C3=A9v, le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s, eg=C3=A9sz napos,<br>
kezd=C5=91 d=C3=A1tum, befejez=C5=91 d=C3=A1tum, sz=C3=ADn</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"681ef0d59dc6">
<p local-id=3D"836dd428586b">Zod valid=C3=A1ci=C3=B3 ut=C3=A1n API h=C3=ADv=
=C3=A1s</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"d053bc9c0f8c">Bejegyz=C3=A9s kateg=C3=B3ri=C3=A1k (EntryCate=
gory):</p>
<ul local-id=3D"21ce7b9867dc">
<li local-id=3D"1f9fb112f83a">
<p local-id=3D"3cd44a655099">None (Nincs)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d48f8c169f50">
<p local-id=3D"147a8f843fd6">Task (Feladat)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48f7d1c1464f">
<p local-id=3D"31322afcf8cc">Event (Esem=C3=A9ny)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1159bffdf65e">
<p local-id=3D"4636000fbca1">BirthDay (Sz=C3=BClet=C3=A9snap)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8a9e076fa57c">
<p local-id=3D"2bb8c692e934">Anniversary (=C3=89vfordul=C3=B3)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"6a7b03f31538">Napt=C3=A1rbejegyz=C3=A9s sz=C3=ADnek:<br>
 12 el=C5=91re defini=C3=A1lt sz=C3=ADn =C3=A1ll rendelkez=C3=A9sre (color1=
-color12), amelyeket a<br>
 calendarColors t=C3=A9ma defini=C3=A1l.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"02795dcc28e6" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-5.6.Kont=
extusmen=C3=BC">5.6. Kontextus men=C3=BC</h2>
<p local-id=3D"afcefe8b92a4">A jobb-klikk kontextus men=C3=BC a ContextMenu=
Store-on kereszt=C3=BCl m=C5=B1k=C3=B6dik:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d4a0394830be">
<li local-id=3D"171c7ed5a355">
<p local-id=3D"9d931e3e6f52">Cella t=C3=ADpus ("cell"): =C3=9Aj bejegyz=C3=
=A9s l=C3=A9trehoz=C3=A1sa</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"acdb8a018b92">
<p local-id=3D"4949bf310b72">Bejegyz=C3=A9s t=C3=ADpus ("schedule"): Bejegy=
z=C3=A9s szerkeszt=C3=A9se/t=C3=B6rl=C3=A9se</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2c382b7bc566">
<p local-id=3D"0013a9066929">Poz=C3=ADci=C3=B3 automatikus igaz=C3=ADt=C3=
=A1sa az ablak sz=C3=A9leihez</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"780c76e15d35">
<p local-id=3D"d2e8b55b239c">Bal klikk a men=C3=BCn k=C3=ADv=C3=BClre bez=
=C3=A1rja</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"082b239beccd" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-5.7.Dial=
=C3=B3gusablakok">5.7. Dial=C3=B3gus ablakok</h2>
