</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0ddb04e34f7c">
<p local-id=3D"428a4c2a6c69">=C3=89rtes=C3=ADt=C3=A9sek list=C3=A1ban t=C3=
=A1rol=C3=B3dnak (notifications t=C3=B6mb)</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"4118907dee9e" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-6.Navig=
=C3=A1ci=C3=B3ss=C3=A1v(Navbar)">6. Navig=C3=A1ci=C3=B3s s=C3=A1v (Navbar)<=
/h1>
<p local-id=3D"c1b1466c7a65">K=C3=A9t v=C3=A1ltozat l=C3=A9tezik az autoriz=
=C3=A1ci=C3=B3 =C3=A1llapot=C3=A1t=C3=B3l f=C3=BCgg=C5=91en:</p>
<p local-id=3D"0e22ea049716">Publikus Navbar (nem bejelentkezett felhaszn=
=C3=A1l=C3=B3):</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6c5c80c93618">
<li local-id=3D"649922539e29">
<p local-id=3D"add3b470903f">Planova log=C3=B3 + alkalmaz=C3=A1s neve</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"73753707f0e2">
<p local-id=3D"d9630e805f8e">"Sign In / Sign Up" gomb</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"436c9e5b8e52">
<p local-id=3D"8572de45c1a5">T=C3=A9ma v=C3=A1lt=C3=B3 gomb (k=C3=B6r alak=
=C3=BA)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"fc1496f6a12e">Priv=C3=A1t Navbar (bejelentkezett felhaszn=C3=
=A1l=C3=B3):</p>
<ul local-id=3D"380d3f328c6c">
<li local-id=3D"e1ec6b4180db">
<p local-id=3D"5729b6caaf76">Hamburger men=C3=BC (oldals=C3=A1v nyit=C3=A1s=
/z=C3=A1r=C3=A1s)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1fb247473bfb">
<p local-id=3D"8433e09b682c">Planova log=C3=B3 + alkalmaz=C3=A1s neve</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"2671073abc5b">
<p local-id=3D"03e79aa6de91">Avatar (kattint=C3=A1sra be=C3=A1ll=C3=ADt=C3=
=A1sok panel)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"bf1f9117eec9">Be=C3=A1ll=C3=ADt=C3=A1sok panel (Popover):</p=
>
<ul local-id=3D"62964db5f516">
<li local-id=3D"4f69b0187fde">
<p local-id=3D"f2b9e9a68402">T=C3=A9ma v=C3=A1lt=C3=B3 (s=C3=B6t=C3=A9t/vil=
=C3=A1gos m=C3=B3d switch)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1006c4b83c38">
<p local-id=3D"853a1d83e7a5">H=C3=A9t kezd=C5=91napja (h=C3=A9tf=C5=91/vas=
=C3=A1rnap toggle)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1ab33891a1cd">
<p local-id=3D"3645c51cba3f">=C3=93ra form=C3=A1tum (12 =C3=B3r=C3=A1s/24 =
=C3=B3r=C3=A1s toggle)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bb06a0589479">
<p local-id=3D"d40a683c6976">Kijelentkez=C3=A9s gomb</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"a47d4f247be1" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-7.Reszpo=
nz=C3=ADvm=C5=B1k=C3=B6d=C3=A9s">7. Reszponz=C3=ADv m=C5=B1k=C3=B6d=C3=A9s<=
/h1>
<p local-id=3D"c004184e7531">A webalkalmaz=C3=A1s reszponz=C3=ADv tervez=C3=
=A9s=C5=B1:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"10608a2cad14">
<li local-id=3D"f40a9bd746fb">
<p local-id=3D"490bf481739b">Desktop (&gt; 1024px): Teljes n=C3=A9zet, olda=
ls=C3=A1v l=C3=A1that=C3=B3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"51a792103d4e">
<p local-id=3D"2a5a82d32e9c">Tablet (768px =E2=80=93 1024px): Oldals=C3=A1v=
 alap=C3=A9rtelmezetten elrejtve,<br>
hamburger men=C3=BCvel megnyithat=C3=B3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a2ebd2a2a67d">
<p local-id=3D"1ccd1e5bf08f">Mobil (&lt; 768px): Mobil n=C3=A9zet, egyszer=
=C5=B1s=C3=ADtett elrendez=C3=A9s</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"682b11f8a39b">Az ablakm=C3=A9ret figyel=C3=A9se az useCalend=
arStore.initResizeListener() f=C3=BCggv=C3=A9nyen<br>
kereszt=C3=BCl t=C3=B6rt=C3=A9nik, amely resize event listener-t regisztr=
=C3=A1l.</p>
