<p local-id=3D"ce71baa6514a">Providers (legk=C3=BCls=C5=91)<br>
 =E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 NextThemeProvider (t=C3=A9ma perzisztencia)<br=
>
 =E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 InnerProviders<br>
 =E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 auth verify (hiteles=C3=ADt=C3=A9s ellen=C5=91=
rz=C3=A9s ind=C3=ADt=C3=A1skor)<br>
 =E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 TamaguiProvider (Tamagui UI keretrendszer)<br>
 =E2=94=82 =E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 QueryClientProvider (React Query cac=
he)<br>
