<h1 local-id=3D"8c24479b1019" id=3D"Frontenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-10.APIv=
=C3=A9gpontok(frontendoldal)">10. API v=C3=A9gpontok (frontend oldal)</h1>
<p local-id=3D"97d18e2efdec">A frontend az al=C3=A1bbi backend API v=C3=A9g=
pontokat haszn=C3=A1lja:</p>
<p local-id=3D"1289ba4eaa76">Autentik=C3=A1ci=C3=B3:<br>
 POST api/auth/sign-up - Regisztr=C3=A1ci=C3=B3<br>
 POST api/auth/sign-in - Bejelentkez=C3=A9s<br>
 GET api/auth/sign-out - Kijelentkez=C3=A9s<br>
 GET api/auth/verify - Token =C3=A9rv=C3=A9nyes=C3=ADt=C3=A9s<br>
 GET api/auth/refresh - Token friss=C3=ADt=C3=A9s</p>
<p local-id=3D"48cd933127db">Napt=C3=A1r:<br>
 GET api/Calendar - Napt=C3=A1rak lek=C3=A9rdez=C3=A9se<br>
 POST api/Calendar - Napt=C3=A1r l=C3=A9trehoz=C3=A1sa<br>
 PUT api/Calendar/{id} - Napt=C3=A1r m=C3=B3dos=C3=ADt=C3=A1sa<br>
 DELETE api/Calendar/{id} - Napt=C3=A1r t=C3=B6rl=C3=A9se</p>
<p local-id=3D"f050180f7aeb">Napt=C3=A1rbejegyz=C3=A9s:<br>
 GET api/CalendarEntry/{id} - Bejegyz=C3=A9sek lek=C3=A9rdez=C3=A9se (sz=C5=
=B1rhet=C5=91 d=C3=A1tummal)<br>
 POST api/CalendarEntry - Bejegyz=C3=A9s l=C3=A9trehoz=C3=A1sa<br>
 PUT api/CalendarEntry/{id} - Bejegyz=C3=A9s m=C3=B3dos=C3=ADt=C3=A1sa<br>
 DELETE api/CalendarEntry/{id} - Bejegyz=C3=A9s t=C3=B6rl=C3=A9se</p>
<p local-id=3D"bad222925dea">Profil:<br>
 GET api/Profile - Profil lek=C3=A9rdez=C3=A9se<br>
 PUT api/Profile/{id} - Profil m=C3=B3dos=C3=ADt=C3=A1sa</p>
<p local-id=3D"28ec633981c7">Bar=C3=A1t k=C3=A9r=C3=A9s:<br>
 POST api/friend-request - Bar=C3=A1t k=C3=A9r=C3=A9s k=C3=BCld=C3=A9se</p>
<p local-id=3D"b04b6a17ea56">SignalR Hub:<br>
 /notifications - Val=C3=B3s idej=C5=B1 =C3=A9rtes=C3=ADt=C3=A9sek (WebSock=
et)</p>
